To commemorate Nigeria’s Democracy Day, President Muhammadu Buhari will broadcast to the nation on Friday, June 12, 2020 at 7am. Television and radio stations as well as other electronic media outlets are enjoined to hook up to the network services of the Nigerian Television Authority and Radio Nigeria respectively for the broadcast. Femi Adesina  Special Adviser to the President (Media and Publicity)  June 11,  2020 Tanimu is an Online Editor with Africa's Largest TV Network. Produces when not on Social media.